name: 5 th International Conference on Applied Sciences, Engineering, Technology And Management
content: Institute For Engineering Research And Publication (IFERP) organizes the “5 th International Conference on Applied Sciences, Engineering, Technology And Management (ICASETM 2022)” on 21st & 22nd April 2022,Dubai, UAE. This conference is a multidisciplinary program with broad participation with members from around the globe focused on learning about the latest trends & research methodologies in Engineering, Science & Management.
organizers: INSTITUTE FOR ENGINEERING RESEARCH AND PUBLICATION (IFERP)
